==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''to effervesce'''
#(''of a liquid'') to [[emit]] small [[bubble]]s of [[dissolved]] [[gas]]; to [[froth]] or [[fizz]]
#(''of a gas'') to [[escape]] from [[solution]] in a [[liquid]] in the form of bubbles
#(''of a person'') to show [[high spirits]]
